ISADIDEKILE indoda yaKwaNongoma eshonelwe yinkosikazi yayo nezingane ezintathu engozini edlule nemiphefumulo yabayisikhombisa eyenzeke eVryheid ngoMgqibelo ekuseni. UMnuz Samuel Ndebele (69) wakwaNgwabi, KwaNongoma, uthe kusenzima ukukholwa wukuthi inkosikazi nezingane zakhe abasekho emhlabeni ngemuva kwenhlekelele yengozi.Uthe ubeqashe imoto ukuthi ihambise izingane nenkosikazi yakhe ekhweni lakhe beyokwenzelwa usiko lokubafaka esibongweni sakhe kanti ubesebabona okokugcina. Ngenxa yemikhuhlane ehlale ihlupha izingane, kungiphoqile ukuthi ngenze izinhlelo zokuyobabuyisela esibongweni sami ngokwesiko. NgoLwesihlanu ngiqashe imoto ukuze ibahambise beyogcina lelo siko behambisana nesangoma ebesijwayele ukusisebenzisa uma kukhona okumele sikwenze okuthinta isiko. Bengithi ngizamela izingane zami impilo engenazinkinga kanti sengizithuma ekufeni, kubalisa uNdebele.Engozini kushone uNkk Nomusa Ndebele (57) nezingane zakhe obekuyizo ebeziyokwenzelwa umsebenzi wokubuyiselwa esibongweni sakubo oMnuz Mfanafuthi Ndebele (29), Mnuz Sifiso Ndebele (35) noNksz Zenanile Ndebele (33), umshayeli wemoto ( esigcine singawutholanga umndeni wakhe) nesangoma uNksz Lindeni Qwabe (36).Kuphinde kwashona noNksz Ncamisile Nhlengethwa (28) ongudadewabo omncane kaNkk Ndebele. UMnuz Elias Qwabe, uyise wesangoma, uthe indodakazi yakhe beyijwayelene kakhulu nomndeni wakwaNdebele ngoba bebejwayele ukumlanda uma kukhona abafuna abenzele khona. Kuthiwa laba bebegibele emotweni eyodwa encane ebisuka eCharlestown ekhweni likaNdebele isibuyela emuva KwaNongoma ukuyophothula umsebenzi. Umthombo weSolezwe ofike kuqala endaweni yengozi, uthe ingozi idalwe yimoto yamakhaza ebihamba umshayeli kuphela. Kuthiwa izame ukusika iloli endaweni okungavumelike ukuthi kusikwe kuyo maqede yatholana phezulu nebihamba lo mndeni. Umshayeli wemoto yamakhaza ulimele waphuthunyiswa esibhedlela.Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu Natal, uCaptain Nqobile Gwala, uthe sekuvulwe icala lokubulala ngokungenhloso esiteshini samaphoyisa esiseVryheid. Kusaphenywa ngembangela yengozi.